reviewText: Its the next best thing if you cant go or a guide of what to expect if you are thinking about going.
This was purchased for my grandsons.  They love Punkin Chunkin.

This is just a fun show.  Boys playing with big toys throwing pumpkins.  I just go back to my youth and laugh at the things these guys do for an oversized statue.  Give it a shot and just enjoy yourself.

Miss having the Mythbusters crew on this but seeing as they did not have the punkin chunkin last year 2014 and it is tradition they day afer Thanksgiving to watch it I bought the DVD and we had fun watching it in its early days.
3 yo grandson watches it every night that he stays with us so we got him his own DVD to take home
We are Chunkin' fans and wait for the latest show each Thanksgiving.  It's fun to have the video to watch for the rest of the year.
